            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Enriched 186W sample in form of WO3 was encapsulated",
                "in synthetic quartz ampoule with inner diameter 3 mm,",
                "outer diameter 5 mm and length of 20 mm. Eight targets",
                "with 186W masses from 1.97 mg to 18.23 mg",
                "were prepared as follows.",
                "                                            Activ 188W",
                "Target No.  186W mass Irrad. time   flux     at EOB",
                "               (mg)               n/cm2/s   MBq/mg 186W",
                "    1         18.23       5 m      2E+14",
                "    2          1.97      55 m      2E+14",
                "    3a         7.89       1 d      2E+15    4.1+-0.8",
                "    3b         7.34       1 d      2E+15    3.3+-0.8",
                "    4a         7.37       5 d    1.95E+15    52+-3",
                "    4b        10.3        5 d    1.95E+15    49+-3",
                "    5a         7.65      10 d      2E+15     96+-6",
                "    5b         8.37      10 d      2E+15    100+-6"
              ]
            },
